Package lgp.core.environment.dataset

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DatasetLoader<TData>
    An extended interface ComponentLoader that loads a class Dataset.
    Target<TData>
    A target output in a class Dataset.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CsvDatasetLoader<TData>
    Loads a collection of samples and their target values from a CSV file.
    CsvDatasetLoaderKt  
    Dataset<TData>
    A basic data set composed of a vector of input class Samples and a collection of output interface Targets.
    Feature<TData>
    A feature of a sample in some data set.
    NominalFeature<TData>  
    ParsingFunctions
    Provides a collection of parsing functions that can be used by a class CsvDatasetLoader instance.
    Sample<TData>
    A sample in a class Dataset made up of a collection of class Features.
    SequenceGenerator
    Can generate a sequence of values evenly spread between a range.
    Targets
    A collection of built-in interface Target implementations
    UniformlyDistributedGenerator
    Can generate a number of uniformly distributed values.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidCsvFileException
    Exception given when a CSV file that does not match the criteria the system expects is given to a class CsvDatasetLoader instance.
    InvalidNumberOfSamplesException
